727279f-a.title: Queens: Liverpool Street - 106th Avenue
727279f-a.text:
Liverpool Street, at the S.W. corner of 106th Avenue,
showing St. 7atrieks Roman Catholic Church.
March 30, 1931
P. L. Sperr

727280f-a.title: Queens: Liverpool Street - 106th Avenue
727280f-a.text:
Liverpool Street, at the N.W. corner of 106th Avenue,
showing Public School No. 165. It was Public School No. 50
in 1909, and No. 50 Annex in 1929.
March 30, 1932
P. L. Sperr
